         Epitome, concerning your Tanking and FearKite spell lineups - I'd drop either Aug or Lich and swap them out when needed. They both have roughly the spell duration so timing them is easy. Plus an extra dot in your lineup will make the XP move faster.</P><P>If I'm not mistaken, I think the Post-Nerf CoS is a 5 sec casting time, same as the spell Gather Shadows.</P><P></P><P>- Ryptor, Heretic of Tunare</P><P>** Quidquid latine dictum sit, altum sonatur **<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
